title: 70s HIIT Elliptical Workout | Elliptical Machine Class to 70s Pop | Fitscope Studio
description:
70s HIIT Elliptical Workout | Elliptical Machine Class to 70s Pop | Fitscope Studio

Join Meghan for this short but intense elliptical machine interval workout. Meghan makes use of both resistance and inclines intervals with a happy 70s pop soundtrack including Sister Sledge, Abba, Elton John, Diana Ross and more. 

Class Plan: 
5 min warmup
4 min intervals
1 min cool down
